sequenceDiagram
    participant User as External Client
    participant Gateway as Istio Ingress Gateway<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.3
    participant VS as Istio VirtualService<br/>Traffic Routing
    participant KnativeSvc as Knative Service<br/>80/TCP HTTP
    participant Activator as Knative Activator<br/>8012/TCP HTTP mTLS
    participant Agent as Agent Sidecar<br/>8080/TCP HTTP
    participant Predictor as Inference Server Pod<br/>8080/TCP HTTP
    participant S3 as S3 Storage<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+

    Note over User,S3: Flow 1: Model Deployment - Serverless Mode

    User->>Gateway: kubectl apply InferenceService<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    Gateway->>Webhook: Validate/Mutate CR<br/>9443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+<br/>Auth: mTLS
    Webhook-->>Gateway: Validated
    Gateway->>Controller: Watch InferenceService CR<br/>Controller reconciles
    Controller->>KnativeSvc: Create Knative Service<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+<br/>Auth: SA Token
    Controller->>S3: storage-initializer downloads model<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+<br/>Auth: AWS IAM/Access Keys
    S3-->>Predictor: Model artifacts loaded

    Note over User,S3: Flow 2: Inference Request - External Client

    User->>Gateway: POST /v1/models/model:predict<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.3<br/>Auth: Bearer Token (optional)
    Gateway->>VS: Route request<br/>Apply traffic policies
    VS->>KnativeSvc: Forward to service<br/>80/TCP HTTP
    KnativeSvc->>Activator: Activate pod if scaled to zero<br/>8012/TCP HTTP<br/>Encryption: mTLS (Istio)
    Activator->>Agent: Inference request<br/>8080/TCP HTTP<br/>Auth: None
    Agent->>Predictor: Batched request<br/>8080/TCP HTTP<br/>Auth: None
    Predictor-->>Agent: Prediction result
    Agent-->>Activator: Response
    Activator-->>KnativeSvc: Response
    KnativeSvc-->>VS: Response
    VS-->>Gateway: Response
    Gateway-->>User: JSON Response<br/>HTTPS

    Note over Agent,Logger: Flow 3: Request Logging (Optional)

    participant Logger as Logger Endpoint<br/>80/443 TCP HTTP/HTTPS
    Agent->>Logger: Log request/response<br/>80/443 TCP HTTP/HTTPS<br/>Auth: Bearer Token (optional)

    Note over Router,Predictor: Flow 4: Multi-Model Inference Graph

    participant Router as InferenceGraph Router<br/>8080/TCP HTTP
    participant Transformer as Transformer Service<br/>80/TCP HTTP mTLS
    participant P1 as Predictor-1<br/>80/TCP HTTP mTLS
    participant P2 as Predictor-2<br/>80/TCP HTTP mTLS

    User->>Router: Inference request<br/>8080/TCP HTTP<br/>Auth: Bearer Token (optional)
    Router->>Transformer: Pre-process<br/>80/TCP HTTP<br/>Encryption: mTLS (Istio)
    Transformer-->>Router: Transformed data
    Router->>P1: Route to Predictor-1<br/>80/TCP HTTP mTLS
    Router->>P2: Route to Predictor-2<br/>80/TCP HTTP mTLS
    P1-->>Router: Prediction-1
    P2-->>Router: Prediction-2
    Router-->>User: Ensemble result
